                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6820" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SCLM-0156</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8220 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">传统采购到战略采购——厦钨新能的数字化采购之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From traditional procurement to strategic procurement：the digital procurement road of XTC New Energy Materials</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">周明，赵婉玲</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东华理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">厦门厦钨新能源材料股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采购供应部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">厦钨新能；战略采购；采购管理；数字化采购平台</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">XTC New Energy Materials; Strategic Procurement; Procurement Management； Digital Procurement Platform</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">面对新能源补贴逐渐退坡，行业竞争加剧等行业环境变化，厦钨新能认识到降低采购成本和保障原材料供应稳定对企业未来发展至关重要，决心构建一个支撑战略采购需求的数字化采购平台。本案例以厦钨新能公司为核心企业，围绕厦钨新能的数字化采购转型项目的实施过程，回顾了实施动因、项目准备和实施过程中面临的挑战及应对策略，重点描述了其与SRM系统服务商用友公司组建项目团队推进数字化采购平台建设及运行的全过程。本案例旨在引导学生思考企业数字化采购转型项目的实施与需要注意的问题，也为想以数字化采购为切入点，推动全面数字化转型的企业提供借鉴参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the face of changes in the industry environment such as the gradual decline of new energy subsidies and the intensification of industry competition, XTC New Energy Materials recognizes that reducing procurement costs and ensuring the stability of raw material supply are crucial to the future development of enterprises, and is determined to build a digital procurement platform that supports strategic procurement needs. Focusing on the implementation process of XTC New Energy Materials&#39; digital procurement transformation project, this case reviewed the implementation motivations, project preparation and implementation challenges and coping strategies in the process of implementation, and focused on the whole process of forming a project team with SRM system service commercial friend company to promote the construction and operation of the digital procurement platform. This case is designed to guide students to think about the implementation of the digital procurement transformation project of enterprises and the issues that need attention, and also provide reference for enterprises that want to use digital procurement as the starting point to promote comprehensive digital transformation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《采购与供应链管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采购转型动因；战略采购的内涵、意义；数字化采购与战略采购的关系；数字化采购平台建设</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
